  "sn56.14:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56",
  "sn56.14:2.1": "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga",
  "sn56.14:3.1": "<span class=\\\"var\\\" title=\\\"āyatanasuttaṃ (bj) | āyatana (pts1)\\\" id=\\\"note528\\\">14. Ajjhattikāyatanasutta</span>",
  "sn56.14:4.1": "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni.",
  "sn56.14:4.2": "Katamāni cattāri?",
  "sn56.14:4.3": "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.14:5.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.14:5.2": "‘Cha ajjhattikāni āyatanānī’tissa vacanīyaṃ.",
  "sn56.14:5.3": "Katamāni cha?",
  "sn56.14:5.4": "Cakkhāyatanaṃ … pe …",
  "sn56.14:5.5": "manāyatanaṃ—",
  "sn56.14:5.6": "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.14:6.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.14:6.2": "Yāyaṃ taṇhā ponobbhavikā nandirāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, seyyathidaṃ—",
  "sn56.14:6.3": "kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā—",
  "sn56.14:6.4": "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.14:7.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.14:7.2": "Yo tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodho cāgo paṭinissaggo mutti anālayo—",
  "sn56.14:7.3": "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.14:8.1": "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ?",
  "sn56.14:8.2": "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—",
  "sn56.14:8.3": "sammādiṭṭhi … pe …",
  "sn56.14:8.4": "sammāsamādhi—",
  "sn56.14:8.5": "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ.",
  "sn56.14:8.6": "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni.",
  "sn56.14:9.1": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe …",
  "sn56.14:9.2": "‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti.",
  "sn56.14:10.1": "Catutthaṃ."
}